org.pathvisio.core.model

Class GpmlFormatAbstract2017

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pathvisio.core.model.GpmlFormatAbstract2017

  • public abstract class GpmlFormatAbstract2017
extends java.lang.Object
    Read / write GPML files. Base implementation for different GpmlFormat revisions. Code that is shared between multiple revisions is located here.
